THE DOGGUY offers obedience / companion training and behavior modification to people with "problem" dogs. Several veterinarians refer canine aggression and biting cases to Chris as their last chance for rehabilitation and management. Chris has no favorite training method or ideology, preferring to utilize the dog's inherent drives and understanding that every dog is different and therefore will have different motivators. The end result is a dog that is spirited and eager to work.
